{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDQ5Mzg1MzA4", "number": 3910, "title": "Add LivingEntity#clearActiveItem", "bodyText": "Prior to 1.16, you could clear a Player's activeItem by calling Player#updateInventory. That method no longer clears the activeItem.\nThis new method LivingEntity#clearActiveItem can be used to interrupt shield blocking, bow drawing, eating and drinking, and possibly other things that I haven't thought about. It calls EntityLiving#clearActiveItem, which is the method used by the server when a player's shield is disabled by being hit with an axe.\nThis is a copy of a previous PR I did, which I chose to discard due to poor branch management by me: #3895", "createdAt": "2020-07-15T10:15:48Z", "url": "https://github.com/PaperMC/Paper/pull/3910", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "fd33bcee19e95e6a6e2c6400c68febdc0e3f6125"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-12-02T20:01:03Z", "author": {"login": "Anrza"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 8, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABc1I77bAFqTQ0ODg2NDExMw==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdiUKyugFqTU0MzE5MTQ5NA==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDQ4ODY0MTEz", "url": "https://github.com/PaperMC/Paper/pull/3910#pullrequestreview-448864113", "createdAt": "2020-07-15T11:28:46Z", "commit": {"oid": "ea3336550e4c189d6a53c1ec924fdd3dca8d4956"}, "state": "DISMISSED", "comments": {"totalCount": 0, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": null, "endCursor": null, "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": []}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTIxMjU1NTI1", "url": "https://github.com/PaperMC/Paper/pull/3910#pullrequestreview-521255525", "createdAt": "2020-11-01T19:56:15Z", "commit": {"oid": "ea3336550e4c189d6a53c1ec924fdd3dca8d4956"}, "state": "DISMISSED", "comments": {"totalCount": 2, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYy